# Smart-Lite Insight

**Edge-AI Energy Monitoring & Anomaly Detection on Raspberry Pi 5**

An end-to-end machine learning pipeline that ingests household energy data, detects anomalies using Isolation Forest, serves predictions via FastAPI, and visualises results in a Streamlit dashboard â€” all running locally on a Raspberry Pi 5 (8 GB).

